  <onto:description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">At Arkansas State University (A-State), full and partial Social Security numbers are compromised for about 50,000 early childhood practitioners after unauthorized access is gained to databases related to the Traveling Arkansas Professional Pathways (TAPP).</onto:description>
